Class Medium

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.dezibel.data.Medium
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Commentable, Lockable

    public class Medium
extends java.lang.Object
implements Commentable, Lockable
    Stores information about a music file, which can be uploaded, played, deleted and locked by fitting users.
    Author:
    Pascal, Bastian, Tobias

      • upload

        public ErrorCode upload(java.lang.String path)
        Uploads the file given by the filepath to our database and makes the medium playable.
        Parameters:
        path - the filepath where the medium which should be uploaded is stored
        Returns:
        returns an errorcode which shows if the upload worked fine or if a problem occured and which kind of problem that was
        Precondition:
        path leads to a valid file
        Postcondition:
        medium is now playabale and upload-date is set to the current date
